but it was somebody just doing

00:37:48.530 --> 00:37:50.160
it on their own.

00:37:50.160 --> 00:37:52.770
Of course, he was making
millions of dollars,

00:37:52.770 --> 00:37:54.030
that probably didn't hurt.

00:37:54.030 --> 00:37:58.340
But along the same lines, just
without the NGOs thrown in,

00:37:58.340 --> 00:38:00.770
just somebody taking
it upon themselves.

00:38:00.770 --> 00:38:01.750
ALEXIS BATEMAN: Well,
if every corporation

00:38:01.750 --> 00:38:03.416
