00:38:05.199 --> 00:38:06.740
Perfect story, I
mean I think there's

00:38:06.740 --> 00:38:07.520
a lot of those examples.

00:38:07.520 --> 00:38:08.910
AUDIENCE: Very, very applicable.

00:38:08.910 --> 00:38:09.320
ALEXIS BATEMAN: Yes.

