00:38:36.360 --> 00:38:38.490
of America, their own--
so it was actually

00:38:38.490 --> 00:38:41.510
internal agitation, it wasn't
an external environmental NGO,

00:38:41.510 --> 00:38:42.980
and that became a huge thing.

00:38:42.980 --> 00:38:45.930
You guys should look it up,
