ALEXIS BATEMAN: What's that?

00:38:47.780 --> 00:38:48.780
AUDIENCE: Did they change it?

00:38:48.780 --> 00:38:50.113
ALEXIS BATEMAN: They did commit.

00:38:50.113 --> 00:38:52.630
They did commit, so they're
