00:38:54.940 --> 00:38:55.700
certification.

00:38:55.700 --> 00:38:59.440
But the actual Girl Scouts who
started when they're like 10

00:38:59.440 --> 00:39:02.194
and are like now about 17
or something, they're like,

00:39:02.194 --> 00:39:04.610
no it's not enough, we want
