00:39:04.610 --> 00:39:06.193
So they're still
pushing the internal.

00:39:06.193 --> 00:39:08.960
So it's a huge media thing.

00:39:08.960 --> 00:39:11.740
But there's-- you can see
where different agitation comes

00:39:11.740 --> 00:39:13.136
in within stakeholders.

00:39:13.136 --> 00:39:14.510
So actually, what
we were talking

00:39:14.510 --> 00:39:17.585
about with the NGOs and the
different types of NGOs,

00:39:17.585 --> 00:39:19.460
you mentioned the
Environmental Defense Fund.

00:39:19.460 --> 00:39:21.600
Actually, next week,
