00:39:38.390 --> 00:39:40.100
to attack.

00:39:40.100 --> 00:39:42.520
So for the rest
of today I thought

00:39:42.520 --> 00:39:47.400
I am going to just kind of
give you a brief overview.

00:39:47.400 --> 00:39:51.870
Anyone else have any
